		<u><h3><a href="https://www.capitolavillage.com/" target="_blank">Capitola Village</a></h3></u>	
			<p>Hidden away about fifteen minutes from the business of downtown Santa Cruz, Capitola Village is a unique spot on the water. Walk along the esplanade and discover great restuarants with spectacular views of the bay. This sweet little spot has it's own beauty. Historic train tracks run acorss the the hill above. Stand on the bridge and get a sweeping view of the water. It's the perfect place to grab some lunch and head to the beach as it's just off the esplanade path.</p>
