		<u><h3><a href="https://www.montereybayaquarium.org/" target="_blank">Monterey Bay Aquarium</a></h3></u>
			<p>Located at the south-end of the bay, The Monterey Bay Aquarium is a must when visiting the central coast. Opened in 1984, this aquarium focuses heavily on marine conversation and wildlife rehabilitation. The aquarium also holds educational programs for those interested in marine ecology. Many different exhibits are offered for viewing so there is something for everyone to see and experience. From penguins to batrays to great white sharks, this aquarium works with a diverse range of animals.</p>
